{"tid":1590961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港共有冇後悔放gohone出來","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:37:31.000Z","uid":40763,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1314c601672164a21dd5e299b8a828b884f7b650","tid":1590961,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"睇住佢放監 即刻去金鍾路祭梁烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n脫隊咁耐 短時間已經跟到大家既步伐 知道大家冇大台 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n係美國戰線唔只靠我地手足舉旗 文宣 登報 仲有佢去美國出席聽證會 遊說 <br />\n坦白講 佢係美國既地位舉足輕重 佩洛西望住佢好似媽媽望仔咁 佢係美國戰線都有一功<br />\n<br />\n當初我都有份笑你 但係估唔到你進步得咁快<br />\n希望你係未來繼續發光發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b06047e5abeb6e63065d3d71192222b27059cc","tid":1590961,"uid":72381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"中共想樹立一個賣港賊黎被人集火<br />\n再除去佢黎撲息個運動<br />\n而家睇黎適得其反<br />\n今次運動，市民既共識真係勝負關鍵"},{"pid":"d17c23d57bb22b8b96118c8426e164ce2b53310c","tid":1590961,"uid":247184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"而家共匪有哂舉動都只會令人民憤"},{"pid":"32f02c0ea156d6fb712ce42a05c9e1167fb98f28","tid":1590961,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08b06047e5abeb6e63065d3d71192222b27059cc","tid":1590961,"uid":72381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"中共想樹立一個賣港賊黎被人集火<br />\n再除去佢黎撲息個運動<br />\n而家睇黎適得其反<br />\n今次運動，市民既共識真係勝負關鍵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打有道理<br />\n點估到佢進化得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c582fd5adfe0f4147e18f5a616ed8eb55aa64b8d","tid":1590961,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"